{"title":"搭建LAMP环境","uid":"065300218eb4a63be27d42f44bfa37db","slug":"搭建LAMP环境","date":"2019-06-14T10:11:41.000Z","updated":"2022-10-24T05:04:11.476Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/搭建LAMP环境.json","keywords":"Brevin, blog, 技术, 博客","cover":"/images/lnmp.png","content":"<h1 id=\"1搭建-MySQL-数据库\"><a href=\"#1搭建-MySQL-数据库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1搭建 MySQL 数据库\"></a>1搭建 MySQL 数据库</h1><p>安装 MySQL<br>使用 yum 安装 MySQL：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install mysql-server -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装完成后，启动 MySQL 服务：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service mysqld restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>设置 MySQL 账户 root 密码：[?]</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/usr/bin/mysqladmin -u root password <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Password&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"2安装-Apache-服务\"><a href=\"#2安装-Apache-服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2安装 Apache 服务\"></a>2安装 Apache 服务</h1><p>安装 Apache<br>使用 yum 安装 Apache</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install httpd -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>启动 Apache 服务：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service httpd start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"3安装-PHP\"><a href=\"#3安装-PHP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3安装 PHP\"></a>3安装 PHP</h1><p>安装 PHP 和 PHP-MYSQL 支持工具：<br>使用 yum 安装 PHP：[?]</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install php php-mysql -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>CentOS 6 默认已经安装了 php-mysql，下面命令执行的可能会提示已经安装。</p>\n<h1 id=\"4检查安装是否成功\"><a href=\"#4检查安装是否成功\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4检查安装是否成功\"></a>4检查安装是否成功</h1><p>检验 PHP 是否安装成功<br>我们在 /var/www/html 目录下创建一个info.php文件来检查php是否安装成功，示例代码参考如下</p>\n<p>示例代码：/var/www/html/info.php</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;?php phpinfo(); ?&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启 Apache 服务：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">service httpd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时，访问 http://&lt;您的 CVM IP 地址&gt;/info.php 可浏览到我们刚刚创建的 info.php 页面了</p>\n","text":"1搭建 MySQL 数据库安装 MySQL使用 yum 安装 MySQL： 1yum install mysql-server -y 安装完成后，启动 MySQL 服务： 1service mysqld restart 设置 MySQL 账户 root 密码：[?] 1/usr/...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":653,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":3,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA-MySQL-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1搭建 MySQL 数据库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-Apache-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2安装 Apache 服务</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%8